name: Metaversel Automation Inc. Logo Design Document 1
description:
Preliminary Logo for Metaversel Automation Inc. An imagined company of the future.

Their products utilize multiple technologies to create Nano Bots that you add to water, and consume. They grant you 48 hours of identity assistance, so that you can restructure your abilities to match who you feel you should be. Strong, smart, beautiful, funny. These traits are programmed to interact with your body on a very low level. Just consume every 48 hours if you'd like to keep the trait. Thousands available. Mix and Match safely, with our intelligent and resourceful designs.


Fake product not meant to resemble any real company, any similarities are not intended by Artist, and no one should mistake this for the reality of anything.
